reviewText: This was a good bargain, except for the fact it was a DVD copy of a VHS that was in so-so condition.  Otherwise, it was an affordable item.

The quality of the movies is worse than terrible. I wish I could have given a "0" to this DVD. Washed out and the Zorro is the French Delon(a respected French actor) and ridiculous Zorro. Monte Cristo is washed out--the sea is white and not blue! I don't know what country makes this disk but DON'T BUY IT ! ! ! ! !
